                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140525-64-off372 t18140525-64-victim602"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , about the hour of two in the night of the <rs id="t18140525-64-cd373" type="crimeDate">9th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140525-64-off372 t18140525-64-cd373"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, five bear skins, value 5 l.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181405250034"></xptr>six hare skins, value 6 s. a fox skin, value 2 s. and a rabbit skin, value 6 d. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18140525-64-person603">
                        George 
                        Collins
                     <interp inst="t18140525-64-person603" type="surname" value="Collins"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18140525-64-person603" type="given" value="George"></interp>
